e\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"crap\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related In August, the dancer's Olympic performance was highly criticized for moves like rolling on her back, spinning on her head with her feet still on the ground and a kangaroo dance, an original move Gunn created.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999706185036287, \"rank\": 2.5929665060979468e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancer's Olympic performance\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"moves\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"her head\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"her feet\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"an original move\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People online questioned how Gunn qualified for the Olympics when she was not awarded points for her performances, leading to theories about Gunn being an \\\"industry plant,\\\" NBC News reported.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999706185036287, \"rank\": 2.5929665060979468e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999706185036287, \"rank\": 2.5929665060979468e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"h